title: Hour 1 - Jimmy G Staying in San Francisco
itunes:title: Hour 1 - Jimmy G Staying in San Francisco
description:
Dan Patrick reacts to the news of Jimmy Garoppolo signing a one-year restructured deal to stay in San Francisco... for now. Dan looks at the implications of this deal on the 49ers and the future of Trey Lance. Plus, Albert Pujols continues his quest for 700 home runs!

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
